responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "106115554F22C272D50D9D8C8A388E0E", "To the of brave knights and priests that gave their life during the Great War of the Undying at the Battle of Highmoor. Here stood the righteousness of Highmoor Abbey against a horde of undead and their minotaur master, the Revenant Reapers. If not for their faith and courage the undying would have claimed a lofty base from which to assault the great city of Aela. May the Seven hold their ashes.   ")
name: MIDD_0015_PTS_GravepeakPassMemorial_3
